name: Sherry Brewer
description:
I’m ready to begin a new chapter in my life.I am a kind loving woman. I’m generous and thoughtful. I give 100% of me. I have a lot of energy and like to work out or play sports. I am also content watching tv at times and snuggling. I’m extremely affectionate and need someone who is the same Looking for someone who enjoys life, makes me smile, who’s kindhearted and is looking to start that new chapter with me. if you think i spark your interest why cant you take a lead and figure out the puzzle and teext me at VIII 0 III V IX IV VI III VIII I, so we could have a better i hope you’re smart enough to figure out the clue..I’m hoping to find my last love i can grow old with no games please.
I want a smart man who is intelligent enough to figure out my puzzle.
